  "prompt": "Which earphones are better under 2000?",
  "response": "There are several great options for earphones under \u20b92000 in India. Here are some popular choices known for their performance, sound quality, and overall value:\n\n1. **realme Buds 2**:\n   - Good sound quality with deep bass.\n   - Tangle-free design with a strong build.\n   - In-line remote for music control and calls.\n\n2. **boAt Bassheads 100**:\n   - Emphasizes bass-heavy sound, ideal for bass lovers.\n   - Lightweight and comfortable design.\n   - Comes with a built-in microphone for calls.\n\n3. **Xiaomi Redmi Earphones**:\n   - Good audio quality with a balanced sound profile.\n   - Metal earbuds for a sturdy build.\n   - Comfortable fit and decent noise isolation.\n\n4. **Samsung Galaxy Buds+**:\n   - Offers a good balance of sound quality and features.\n   - Long battery life and comfortable fit.\n   - Good for calls and media consumption.\n\n5. **OnePlus Bullets Z Bass Edition**:\n   - Strong bass performance.\n   - Fast charging feature.\n   - Comfortable design with decent battery life.\n\n6. **Noise Shots NEO**:\n   - True wireless option within this budget.\n   - Good sound quality with a decent battery life.\n   - Comfortable fit for extended wear.\n\n7. **Zebronics Zeb-Rush**:\n   - Good sound quality and design.\n   - In-line remote and a strong bass focus.\n   - Comfortable for long listening sessions.\n\nWhile choosing earphones, consider factors like sound quality, comfort, build quality, and any specific features you might want (like a mic, in-line controls, or water resistance). Checking customer reviews and ratings can also help in making a more informed decision.",
